location.name: Home 3/St. Charles Rd./Prairie Ave./Western Ave./Winslow Cir./Pleasant Ave.

mediaNotes: Longish file demonstrating the behavior of a Red-bellied Woodpecker at a potential nesting cavity.  A one or two note call answered by a more distant bird, plus drumming.  This call sequence has been used for the past week or more at this location. The file is a blend of two recordings within seconds of one another to get the drumming.  The cadence is intact with the exception of  brief human interruption and a dog bark.  Normalization to -6dBA  One pass with noise reduction to attenuate the background.
